### Verificar que el servidor está funcionando
GET http://localhost:8080/
Accept: application/json

### ==========================================
### AUTENTICACIÓN
### ==========================================

### Registrar un nuevo docente
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "curp": "ABCD123456HDFXXX01",
  "nombres": "Juan Carlos",
  "apellidoPaterno": "García",
  "apellidoMaterno": "López",
  "email": "juan.garcia@escuela.edu.mx",
  "password": "MiPassword123"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "juan.garcia@escuela.edu.mx",
  "password": "MiPassword123"
}

### Guardar el token de la respuesta anterior
### Reemplaza "TU_TOKEN_AQUI" con el token que recibiste

### ==========================================
### ALUMNOS
### ==========================================

### Obtener todos los alumnos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/alumnos
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Obtener alumnos filtrados por grado y grupo
GET http://localhost:8080/api/alumnos?grado=1&grupo=A
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Obtener alumno por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/alumnos/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Crear un nuevo alumno
POST http://localhost:8080/api/alumnos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "curp": "EFGH123456MDFYYY02",
  "nombres": "María",
  "apellidoPaterno": "Pérez",
  "apellidoMaterno": "Sánchez",
  "fechaNacimiento": "2010-05-15",
  "grado": 1,
  "grupo": "A"
}

### Actualizar un alumno
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/alumnos/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "curp": "EFGH123456MDFYYY02",
  "nombres": "María Fernanda",
  "apellidoPaterno": "Pérez",
  "apellidoMaterno": "Sánchez",
  "fechaNacimiento": "2010-05-15",
  "grado": 2,
  "grupo": "B"
}

### Desactivar un alumno (soft delete)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/alumnos/1
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI

